snippet.title: RPG Tycoon: Supply & Demand Expansion - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Your kingdom has gotten greedy and no longer will simple gold satisfy the needs of your people.

Scheduled for release on November 18th, RPG Tycoon: Supply & Demand brings an array of new features to the game. Including trading, resource management, a brand new scenario mode and more!

For more information head to http://www.rpgtycoon.com/spdm

Don't forget to subscribe and follow the blog for more updates!
http://www.skatanicstudios.co.uk/blog/
